FRANK LAMPARD left a big impression on Chelsea midfielder Ruben Loftus-Cheek.<br />
<br />
He told Chelsea's website: &quot;When he was here I was lucky enough to train with the first team quite a few times so I watched him closely because we played in the same position. He&rsquo;s a massive icon for English football and it was brilliant to be able to learn from him.&quot;
